title: Bike Magazine - January 2014
description:
Bike Magazine - January 2014

138 Pages | True PDF | English | 37 MB 


The Bible of Bike Tests - We travel to Sedona, Arizona, to test 34 of the year's best mountain bikes, as well as wheels, forks, dropper posts, tires and groupsets for the fifth year of the Bible of Bike Tests, the most comprehensive and honest gear guide on the market. Read how top cross country, all mountain and downhill bikes performed on the rigorous test loops set against Sedona's dramatic desert landscape.
